sequenceDiagram
    participant Writer
    participant Buyer
    participant Platform
    participant Oracle

    Writer->>Platform: Deposit BTC
    Writer->>Platform: Create offer (strike as % above spot)
    Buyer->>Platform: Accept offer and pay premium
    Platform->>Oracle: Get BTC/USD
    Oracle-->>Platform: Spot price
    Platform->>Platform: Lock USD strike from % and spot
    Platform-->>Writer: Premium credited, collateral committed
    Note over Platform: At expiry
    Platform->>Oracle: Get BTC/USD at expiry
    alt BTC above strike
        Platform-->>Buyer: Pay profit in BTC
        Platform-->>Writer: Return remaining BTC
    else BTC at or below strike
        Platform-->>Writer: Return full BTC
    end
